 and application launching\",\n        \"Windows 10 and Windows 11 compatible (32-bit and 64-bit)\",\n        \"Compatible with Microsoft 365, Google Docs, and professional applications\"\n      ],\n      \"faqs\": [\n        { \"q\": \"Does Dragon Professional 16 require an internet connection?\", \"a\": \"No. After installation and activation, Dragon Professional 16 works offline. An internet connection is only required for the initial download and product activation.\" },\n        { \"q\": \"How many computers can I use Dragon on?\", \"a\": \"Dragon Professional 16 can be installed on up to 2 Windows computers under a single licence.\" },\n        { \"q\": \"Can I transcribe multi-speaker recordings or meetings?\", \"a\": \"Dragon Professional 16 is designed for single-speaker audio only. It will not reliably transcribe meetings, interviews, or multi-speaker conversations. Supported formats include MP3, WAV, WMA, DS2, and DSS.\" },\n        { \"q\": \"Is this a subscription or permanent purchase?\", \"a\": \"This is a perpetual licence - a one-time purchase. You own it permanently with no annual renewal fees or subscription charges.\" }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"slug\": \"cloud-speech-solutions\",\n      \"heroImageKey\": \"src-hero\",\n      \"featureImageKey\": \"src-feature\",\n      \"badge\": \"Best Free Speech Recognition\",\n      \"navLabel\": \"Cloud Speech-to-Text\",\n      \"title\": \"SpeechRecognition.cloud\",\n      \"metaTitle\": \"Best Free Speech Recognition Software | SpeechRecognition.cloud | VRA\",\n      \"metaDesc\": \"Best speech recognition software in the browser - free tier, 57 languages, no install. Professional and medical tiers for Australian businesses and healthcare teams.\",\n      \"headline\": \"SpeechRecognition.cloud - Best Free Speech Recognition Software\",\n      \"subheadline\": \"Browser-based speech recognition powered by AI. No software to install. 57 languages supported. Free tier available. The best speech to text software for individuals and teams who want to get started without upfront cost.\",\n      \"price\": \"From Free\",\n      \"priceNote\": \"Free tier available - professional and medical subscriptions\",\n      \"licenceNote\": \"Cloud-based. No installation required. Pay-as-you-go or subscription options.\",\n      \"installLimit\": \"Browser-based\",\n      \"bestFor\": \"Cloud-first users - free tier available\",\n      \"vraUrl\": \"https://www.speechrecognition.cloud\",\n      \"ctaText\": \"Visit SpeechRecognition.cloud\",\n      \"features\": [\n        \"Browser-based - works on any device with a web browser\",\n        \"57 languages supported - global and regional dialects\",\n        \"Free tier for individuals and teams to get started\",\n        \"Professional tier - higher accuracy, priority support, API access\",\n        \"Medical tier - healthcare vocabulary, privacy controls, compliance features\",\n        \"Real-time dictation and audio file transcription\",\n        \"No local software installation - instant access\",\n        \"Cloud storage of transcriptions with privacy controls\",\n        \"Team collaboration and sharing features\"\n      ],\n      \"faqs\": [\n        { \"q\": \"Do I need to install software?\", \"a\": \"No. SpeechRecognition.cloud is entirely browser-based. Just log in from any device and start dictating or uploading audio files.\" },\n        { \"q\": \"Is there a free option to try?\", \"a\": \"Yes. A free tier is available with usage limits. Upgrade to Professional or Medical tier for higher usage allowances and priority support.\" },\n        { \"q\": \"How many languages are supported?\", \"a\": \"57 languages are supported including major languages, regional dialects, and specialized medical and legal terminology.\" },\n        { \"q\": \"Is the Medical tier suitable for clinical use?\", \"a\": \"The Medical tier includes healthcare-specific vocabulary, enhanced privacy controls, and compliance features suitable for healthcare environments. Consult the platform for specific compliance certifications.\" }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"slug\": \"dragon-medical-one\",\n      \"heroImageKey\": \"dmo-hero\",\n      \"featureImageKey\": \"dmo-feature\",\n      \"badge\": \"Cloud Healthcare Documentation\",\n      \"navLabel\": \"Dragon Medical One\",\n      \"title\": \"Dragon Medical One\",\n      \"metaTitle\": \"Dragon Medical One Australia | AI Clinical Documentation | VRA\",\n      \"metaDesc\": \"Dragon Medical One - cloud-based AI clinical documentation for Australian doctors. Ambient AI for patient notes. HIPAA-aligned. Medical terminology built-in. Contact Voice Recognition Australia.\",\n      \"headline\": \"Dragon Medical One - AI-Powered Clinical Documentation\",\n      \"subheadline\": \"Cloud-based speech recognition designed for healthcare. Ambient AI captures consultations and generates structured clinical notes. Reduces documentation burden and after-hours work for clinicians.\",\n      \"price\": \"Enquire\",\n      \"priceNote\": \"Annual subscription - contact for Australian pricing\",\n      \"licenceNote\": \"Cloud-based subscription. No local installation required. Access from any device.\",\n      \"installLimit\": \"Unlimited devices\",\n      \"bestFor\": \"Healthcare professionals and practices\",\n      \"vraUrl\": \"https://www.voicerecognition.com.au/pages/dragon-medical-one\",\n      \"ctaText\": \"Request Dragon Medical One Quote\",\n      \"features\": [\n        \"Ambient AI - captures consultation audio and generates structured clinical notes\",\n        \"Built-in medical vocabulary - cardiology, radiology, pathology, and 40+ specialties\",\n        \"Integrates with major Australian practice management systems\",\n        \"HIPAA-aligned for healthcare data security and privacy\",\n        \"Cloud-based - accessible from any device, no desktop software needed\",\n        \"Automatic transcription and note structuring (SOAP format)\",\n        \"Supports dictation in real-time or from voice recordings\",\n        \"Reduces clinical documentation time and after-hours work\",\n        \"Annual subscription model - professional and enterprise tiers\"\n      ],\n      \"faqs\": [\n        { \"q\": \"Is Dragon Medical One available in Australia?\", \"a\": \"Yes. Dragon Medical One is available through Voice Recognition Australia, an authorised Nuance/Microsoft reseller. It is a cloud-based subscription product designed specifically for healthcare documentation.\" },\n        { \"q\": \"What is ambient AI and how does it work?\", \"a\": \"Ambient AI captures consultation audio and automatically generates structured clinical notes without the clinician having to actively dictate or interact with software. This reduces documentation burden and allows clinicians to focus on patient care.\" },\n        { \"q\": \"Do I need local software installation?\", \"a\": \"No. Dragon Medical One is cloud-based. You access it through a web browser on any device - no desktop software installation required.\" },\n        { \"q\": \"What practice management systems does it integrate with?\", \"a\": \"Dragon Medical One integrates with leading Australian practice systems. Contact Voice Recognition Australia for specific integration compatibility with your system.\" }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"slug\": \"philips-speechlive\",\n      \"heroImageKey\": \"psl-hero\",\n      \"featureImageKey\": \"psl-feature\",\n      \"badge\": \"Cloud Dictation Workflow\",\n      \"navLabel\": \"Philips SpeechLive\",\n      \"title\": \"Philips SpeechLive\",\n      \"metaTitle\": \"Philips SpeechLive Australia | Cloud Dictation Workflow | VRA\",\n      \"metaDesc\": \"Philips SpeechLive cloud dictation workflow for Australian healthcare and legal professionals. Dictate from any device, route to transcription, integrate with Dragon. Authorised reseller.\",\n      \"headline\": \"Philips SpeechLive - Cloud Dictation Workflow\",\n      \"su